<p><strong>Helpers</strong>
<code>ruby
helpers do
  ...code...
end
</code></p>

<p><strong>Before filter</strong>
<code>ruby
before do
  ...code...
end
</code></p>

<p><strong>Halt the request</strong>
<code>
halt erb(:index)
</code></p>

<p>For more information, check out its <a href="http://www.sinatrarb.com/intro.html">official intro</a>.</p>
